commit.message: Support old style classes that don't have __mro__.

Merge pull request #6 from jakirkham/inc_license

Package the license file
copy license file from CPython (since it would be nonsense to try to establish a different license for code copied from their stdlib)
make ABCs available directly from the backports_abc module namespace
do not patch inspect.iscoroutine() as it is not ABC based
keep track of what was patched
change usage to require an explicit patch() call instead of just an import with side-effects
also provide inspect.iscoroutine() and inspect.isawaitable() if missing
